00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:19.990
have the opportunity to give you a

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.150
positive word, an uplifting word, an

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:24.429
encouraging word that people have

00:00:24.439 --> 00:00:28.109
